files.pyproject.toml:
[build-system]
requires = ["hatchling"]
build-backend = "hatchling.build"

[project]
name = "qgis-manage"
version = "0.6.3"
description = "A modern CLI for managing QGIS plugin development, deployment, and packaging."
readme = "README.md"
requires-python = ">=3.10"
license = { text = "GPL-2.0-or-later" }
authors = [
    { name = "Juan M Bernales", email = "juanbernales@gmail.com" }
]
keywords = ["qgis", "plugin", "manager", "cli", "development"]
classifiers = [
    "Development Status :: 4 - Beta",
    "Intended Audience :: Developers",
    "Intended Audience :: Science/Research",
    "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU General Public License v2 or later (GPLv2+)",
    "Operating System :: OS Independent",
    "Programming Language :: Python :: 3",
    "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10",
    "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11",
    "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12",
    "Topic :: Scientific/Engineering :: GIS",
    "Topic :: Software Development :: Build Tools",
    "Environment :: Console",
    "Natural Language :: Spanish",
]
dependencies = [
    "click>=8.0",
]

[project.urls]
Homepage = "https://github.com/geociencio/qgis-plugin-manager"
Repository = "https://github.com/geociencio/qgis-plugin-manager"
Issues = "https://github.com/geociencio/qgis-plugin-manager/issues"
Changelog = "https://github.com/geociencio/qgis-plugin-manager/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md"
Documentation = "https://github.com/geociencio/qgis-plugin-manager#readme"

[project.optional-dependencies]
dev = [
    "mypy>=1.19.1",
    "pre-commit>=4.5.1",
    "ruff>=0.14.10",
    "types-setuptools>=80.9.0.20251223",
    "ai-context-core>=3.2.1",
    "qgis-plugin-analyzer>=1.10.0",
]

[project.scripts]
qgis-manage = "qgis_manager.cli:main"

[tool.hatch.build.targets.wheel]
packages = ["src/qgis_manager"]

[tool.hatch.build.targets.sdist]
exclude = [
    "/.agent",
    "/.github",
    "/.vscode",
    "/.pre-commit-config.yaml",
    "/.gitattributes",
    "/.ai_context_cache.json",
    "/AI_CONT
